      <title>拜登为允许乌克兰使用美国武器打击俄罗斯的举动辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-defends-move-to-let-ukraine-hit-russia-with-us-weapons</link>
