    <item>
      <title>分析显示，无论谁赢得英国大选，都需要加税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/tax-rises-needed-whoever-wins-uk-election-analysis-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博经济研究分析称，无论是首相里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）还是在民调中领先的工党对手基尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）都没有以可靠的经济政策来应对英国大选，无论谁获胜，都可能不得不违背不加税的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/tax-rises-needed-whoever-wins-uk-election-analysis-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
